// /// Fusion Standard Collections.
// /// 
// /// These types wrap standard Rust collections to provide:
// /// 1. Integration with Fusion's Error system.
// /// 2. Functional programming utilities (map, filter, reduce).
// /// 3. Future compatibility with the Fusion Memory Allocator.
